'''Sidny Lopes Cabral''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈsid.ni ˈlɔ.pɨʃ kɐ.ˈbɾal|lang}}; born 18 September 2002) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] for [[Primeira Liga]] club [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]. Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].

==Early life==

As a youth player, Cabral joined the youth academy of Swedish side [[Helsingborgs IF|Helsingborg]]. He was regarded as a bright prospect whilst playing for the club's youth team.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gasetten.se/helsingborgs-if/de-15-storsta-talangerna-i-hif-snart-kommer-flera-starka-argangar/|title=De 15 största talangerna i HIF: Snart kommer flera starka årgångar|publisher=gasetten.se}}</ref>

==Club career==

In 2024, Cabral signed for German side [[FC Viktoria Köln|Viktoria Köln]]. He was described as a key part of the club's newfound defensive stability.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ksta.de/sport/viktoria-koeln/mit-viererkette-und-sidny-lopes-cabral-die-neue-stabilitaet-des-fc-viktoria-koeln-733814|title=Die neue Stabilität des FC Viktoria Köln|publisher=ksta.de}}</ref>

In the summer of 2025, Cabral moved to Portugal, signing a three-year contract through to 2028 with [[Primeira Liga]] club [[C.F. Estrela da Amadora|Estrela da Amadora]]. Cabral became an offensive weapon for his new club in his debut season, registering 5 goals and providing 2 assists in the league, the highlight being a hat-trick scored in a game away at [[Casa Pia A.C.|Casa Pia]].<ref>{{Cite web |last= |first= |date=12 June 2025 |title=Sidny Cabral é reforço do Estrela da Amadora |trans-title=Sidny Cabral is a Estrela da Amadora reinforcement |url=https://estrelamadora.pt/sidny-cabral-e-reforco-do-estrela-da-amadora/ |access-date=8 December 2025 |publisher=[[C.F. Estrela da Amadora|Estrela da Amadora]] |language=pt-PT}}</ref>

After impressing during the first half of the season with Estrela, on 30 December 2025, Cabral joined fellow Primeira Liga side [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]], signing a contract until June 2030 for a reported fee of €6 million, which could rise to €8.5 million with add-ons.<ref>{{Cite web |date=30 December 2025 |title=Lopes Cabral é reforço do Benfica! |trans-title=Lopes Cabral is a Benfica reinforcement! |url=https://www.slbenfica.pt/pt-pt/agora/noticias/2025/12/30/futebol-benfica-lopes-cabral-reforco-contratacao-ate-2030 |access-date=30 December 2025 |publisher=[[S.L. Benfica]] |language=pt}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=30 December 2025 |title=Benfica: o valor da cláusula de rescisão de Sidny Cabral |trans-title=Benfica: Sidny Cabral's release clause value |url=https://www.abola.pt/noticias/benfica-o-valor-da-clausula-de-rescisao-de-sidny-cabral-2025123022064479053 |access-date=30 December 2025 |publisher=[[A Bola]] |language=pt}}</ref> He made his debut on 4 January 2026, coming on as a substitute during the second half and assisting [[Vangelis Pavlidis]] for his hat-trick goal in a 3–1 league victory over [[G.D. Estoril Praia|Estoril]] at the [[Estádio da Luz]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=3 January 2026 |title=Sidny e a estreia no Benfica: «Nem sei que dizer!» |trans-title=Sidny and the debut for Benfica: «I don't even know what to say!» |url=https://www.abola.pt/noticias/sidny-e-a-estreia-no-benfica-nem-sei-que-dizer-2026010320205274347 |access-date=4 January 2026 |website=A Bola |language=pt}}</ref> On 25 January, Cabral scored his first goal for Benfica, the third in a 4–0 league victory over his former club Estrela da Amadora.<ref>{{Cite web |last= |date=25 January 2026 |title=Lopes Cabral fez primeiro golo pelo Benfica contra... o Estrela: «Foi um bocadinho estranho» |trans-title=Lopes Cabral scored first goal for Benfica against... Estrela: «It was a little bit weird» |url=https://sapo.pt/artigo/lopes-cabral-fez-primeiro-golo-pelo-benfica-contra-o-estrela-foi-um-bocadinho-estranho-69767f4b1b2f4b1aa6cdbbed |access-date=25 January 2026 |website=SAPO |language=pt}}</ref>

In June 2026, Benfica agreed to transfer Sidny Cabral to Turkish club Trabzonspor for a reported fee of €10 million, with the player arriving in Turkey to complete the move.<ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=3 June 2026 |title=Já está na Turquia a primeira venda do Benfica |url=https://www.abola.pt/noticias/ja-esta-na-turquia-a-primeira-venda-do-benfica-video-2026060310340023018 |access-date=4 June 2026 |work=[[A Bola]] |language=pt}}</ref>

==International career==

Cabral is a Cape Verde international. He was first called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]] for a friendly against [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] in 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thueringer-allgemeine.de/sport/fussball/regionalliga/article239736589/Sidny-Cabral-vom-FC-Rot-Weiss-Erfurt-vor-Debuet-im-Nationaltrikot.html|title=Sidny Cabral vom FC Rot-Weiß Erfurt vor Debüt im Nationaltrikot|publisher=thueringer-allgemeine.de}}</ref>

Cabral scored his first international goal on 29 May 2025 in a friendly against [[Malaysia national football team|Malaysia]] at the [[Kuala Lumpur Stadium]].<ref>{{NFT player}}</ref>

==Style of play==

Cabral mainly operates as a defender. He can operate as a left-back or right-back.

==Personal life==
Cabral was born in 2003 in the [[Netherlands]]. He is the younger brother of Cape Verde international [[Rodny Lopes Cabral]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voetbalzone.nl/nieuws/afvaller-van-fc-twente-duikt-op-bij-zesvoudig-kampioen-kippenvel/386776|title=Afvaller van FC Twente duikt op bij zesvoudig kampioen: 'Kippenvel'|publisher=voetbalzone.nl}}</ref>

